title: All Documents On File (Central Intelligence Agency)

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records: Any and all records pertaining to Mason C. Turner DOB June 2, 1997

There should not be any fees associated pertaining to this request, I would prefer the request be filled electronically, by e-mail attachment and/or download link as allowed per law.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 15 business days.

Sincerely,

Mason C. Turner
6072 SE Crooked Oak Ave, Hobe Sound FL
STE: 201
TurnerMason@gmail.com
Phone: 561-320-7690
Facsimile: 561-258-8351
